modules.description: Handles loading and unloading of LADSPA plugins from shared object files. Works with plugin handles represented as `t` values. Used to dynamically access audio processing functionality provided by external LADSPA libraries.

This module provides operations to load and interact with LADSPA plugins through shared object files, allowing dynamic access to audio processing functions. It works with plugin handles and descriptors to retrieve information about available plugins and their capabilities. Concrete use cases include discovering audio effects or synthesizers at runtime and integrating them into audio processing pipelines.
